The paper deals with mechanism design, which is a subfield of game theory (cs.GT). It also involves optimization and allocation of resources, which are topics in data structures (cs.DS) and machine learning (cs.LG). The concept of Bayesian incentive compatibility is related to information theory (cs.IT). Finally, the paper deals with economic models and market mechanisms, which are topics in computational economics (cs.EC).
